    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and restoration lovers! This vehicle is the perfect blank canvas for your next big project. While it currently requires significant mechanical and cosmetic attention to get back on the road, it offers a fantastic opportunity for someone looking to build their dream car from the ground up or seeking a valuable source of parts. Bring your tools and your vision to give this car a second lease on life!",
